data.description: Charming townhouse nestled in a peaceful location. This 4 bedroom townhome has a single car attached garage and 2 reserved parking spaces. The 4th non-conforming bedroom is in the basement. Don't miss almost 1,800 square feet of finished living space make this townhome a real find at this price.  Take advantage of the large common area for the family to play just outside your back patio. Don't miss the rustic wood burning fireplace in the family room and gorgeous hardwood floors. Come see the perfect home for your family to grow in. WOW! all the appliances and window coverings are included. The location of this home is highly desirable, with close proximity to I76, providing convenient commuting options. Whether you're heading to work, running errands, or exploring the surrounding areas, you'll appreciate the easy access to major transportation routes and near-by shopping. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your family's home!
